            Team
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-2/3">
        <div class="lg:flex ">
          <div class=" flex-1 p-3 relative mt-20">
            <div class=" bottom-2 max-w-full">
              <img src="https://d2kq0urxkarztv.cloudfront.net/593641fc4ac3e7290178b1b1/4083208/upload-5a8ac1bf-3770-464f-a456-aa6eca1ed723.png?e=webp&nll=true" alt="" class="w-80 py-2 m-auto rounded-t-full" >
              <img src="https://d2kq0urxkarztv.cloudfront.net/593641fc4ac3e7290178b1b1/4083208/upload-79210371-67ec-46be-816b-5ce286028827.png?e=webp&nll=true&cX=50&cY=0&cW=435.2535885167464&cH=548" alt="" class="w-80 py-2 m-auto rounded-t-full" >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 p-3 relative mt-20">
            <div class="  text-[0.6rem] xl:text-[0.8rem] px-2">
        
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800">Juan Muiño + Fernando Oltolina</span>
